            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間05日11:08，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>下跌485.14點（或1%），暫報48254.27點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：-1.5%</li><li>近 1 月：-1.54%</li><li>近 3 月：+1.86%</li><li>近 6 月：+6.83%</li><li>今年以來：+1.41%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>成分股以沃爾瑪(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:WMT:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/WMT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">WMT-US</a>)領跌。沃爾瑪(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:WMT:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/WMT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">WMT-US</a>)下跌2.58%；默克藥廠(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MRK:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MRK\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MRK-US</a>)下跌2.54%；嬌生(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:JNJ:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/JNJ\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">JNJ-US</a>)下跌2.13%；寶潔(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:PG:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/PG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">PG-US</a>)下跌1.75%；宣偉(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:SHW:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga