            "title": "盤中速報 - Crowdstrike控股(CRWD-US)大漲5.03%，報428.18美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Crowdstrike控股(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CRWD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CRWD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CRWD-US</a>)截至台北時間05日22:51股價上漲20.5美元，報428.18美元，漲幅5.03%，成交量1,035,988（股），盤中最高價428.26美元、最低價407.00美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-0.78%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-0.24%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-0.01%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+0.03%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>Crowdstrike控股(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CRWD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CRWD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CRWD-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+7.74%</li> <li>近 1 月：-5.76%</li> <li>近 3 月：-23.72%</li> <li>近 6 月：-5.1%</li> <li>今年以來：-16.5%</li></ul></section></main>",
